one that is only hers to make.

52
00:02:13,394 --> 00:02:14,830
- Yeah, but--
- Ah-ah, no "buts."

53
00:02:14,873 --> 00:02:17,441
No meddling, no prying.

54
00:02:17,485 --> 00:02:18,790
You can't even ask.

55
00:02:18,834 --> 00:02:20,618
- So,

56
00:02:20,662 --> 00:02:22,185
what can I do?

57
00:02:22,229 --> 00:02:25,449
- Whatever you need to do
to not talk to her about it,

58
00:02:25,493 --> 00:02:28,322
you should do that.

59
00:02:31,890 --> 00:02:33,588
- There you are.

60
00:02:33,631 --> 00:02:35,677
- Sorry I didn't call you back.

61
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:37,635
It's been a crazy morning.

62
00:02:37,679 --> 00:02:38,897
- Seems like
all your mornings are crazy.

63
