our wedding together.

68
00:02:52,694 --> 00:02:55,305
- Can't wait.

69
00:02:55,349 --> 00:02:57,307
- Well, sounds like you can.

70
00:02:57,351 --> 00:02:59,396
- No.
I'm sorry.

71
00:02:59,440 --> 00:03:01,964
