- Oh.

263
00:11:36,347 --> 00:11:38,959
- I'm scheduled to fly out
on Expedition 64

264
00:11:39,002 --> 00:11:40,264
to the
International Space Station

265
00:11:40,308 --> 00:11:42,223
in 58 weeks.

266
00:11:42,266 --> 00:11:44,747
I've been working toward this
my entire life.

267
00:11:44,791 --> 00:11:47,707
This is my first space mission,

268
00:11:47,750 --> 00:11:50,274
so nothing can be wrong
with my heart.

269
00:12:02,112 --> 00:12:05,072
Uh, what are you doing?

270
00:12:05,115 --> 00:12:06,769
- Mm.

271
00:12:06,813 --> 00:12:08,858
- Earth to Vijay.

272
00:12:08,902 --> 00:12:11,774
- I am meditating.

273
00:12:11,818 --> 00:12:14,603
- Okay.
