274
00:12:14,646 --> 00:12:17,040
- To control
the chaos in my mind.

275
00:12:17,084 --> 00:12:19,173
Because I cannot
talk to someone

276
00:12:19,216 --> 00:12:22,829
I desperately want to talk to.

277
00:12:22,872 --> 00:12:24,395
- Well, that sounds
completely pointless,

278
00:12:24,439 --> 00:12:25,788
but you know what?

279
00:12:25,832 --> 00:12:28,095
I am desperate,
so I'm gonna give it a go.

280
00:12:28,138 --> 00:12:30,662
Come on, help me up here.

281
00:12:35,972 --> 00:12:38,801
- Okay, now fold your legs.
Sorry.

282
00:12:38,845 --> 00:12:41,761
Close your eyes and breathe.

283
00:12:46,983 --> 00:12:48,724
- I'm sorry, do you have
to breathe so loud?

284
00:12:48,768 --> 00:12:50,291
- Mm!

285
00:12:57,864 --> 00:12:59,126
- Hello, this is Aneel.

286
00:12:59,169 --> 00:13:02,085
- Aneel Jay who works
