287
00:13:02,129 --> 00:13:03,260
of Barcroft Insurance?

288
00:13:03,304 --> 00:13:04,696
- Uh, yes.

289
00:13:04,740 --> 00:13:05,785
- Who works
in the appeals department

290
00:13:05,828 --> 00:13:06,829
on the seventh floor?

291
00:13:06,873 --> 00:13:08,352
- Can I help you
with something?

292
00:13:08,396 --> 00:13:10,180
- Yeah, uh, could you remind me
of your office number?

293
00:13:10,224 --> 00:13:13,227
- 728.
What is this regarding?

294
00:13:13,270 --> 00:13:15,098
Hold on.
Yeah?

295
00:13:15,142 --> 00:13:17,361
- Hey, it's regarding the
extremely impersonal practice

296
00:13:17,405 --> 00:13:19,146
of trying to help someone
over the phone.

297
00:13:19,189 --> 00:13:20,843
I just think nothing
really gets done

298
00:13:20,887 --> 00:13:22,149
until you sit down with someone
face to face.

299
00:13:22,192 --> 00:13:23,715
You know what I mean?

300
00:13:23,759 --> 00:13:25,282
- I was just leaving for lunch.
- Were you?

301
00:13:25,326 --> 00:13:26,849
I know a great place.

302
00:13:26,893 --> 00:13:29,112
The honey yogurt's really good
if you want to try it.

303
00:13:29,156 --> 00:13:32,028
- Look, it was
an abrupt change, I know,

304
00:13:32,072 --> 00:13:33,856
but last year,
Barcroft hemorrhaged

305
00:13:33,900 --> 00:13:36,859
an unprecedented $80 million
in surrogacy coverage.

306
00:13:36,903 --> 00:13:40,080
- Sure, but how many babies did
you help bring into the world?

307
00:13:40,123 --> 00:13:41,211
- We don't track
that kind of data.

308
00:13:41,255 --> 00:13:42,909
- Mm.

309
00:13:42,952 --> 00:13:45,215
That's why I brought you here.

310
00:13:45,259 --> 00:13:47,261
Your company gives you data.

311
00:13:47,304 --> 00:13:49,176
You get case numbers
instead of stories.

312
00:13:49,219 --> 00:13:53,397
You get account numbers
instead of people.

313
00:13:58,054 --> 00:13:59,012
- What is this?

314
00:13:59,055 --> 00:14:02,058
- This is account number 42118.

315
00:14:02,102 --> 00:14:04,844
- Her name is Paz Aquino.

316
00:14:07,194 --> 00:14:08,760
- Excuse me.

317
00:14:12,242 --> 00:14:14,723
- Hey, Aneel?

318
00:14:14,766 --> 00:14:16,377
- And people say
insurance companies are cruel?

319
00:14:16,420 --> 00:14:19,467
- I'm just trying to show you--
