a full hysterectomy.

472
00:21:39,167 --> 00:21:41,517
Once we remove the cancer
from your body,

473
00:21:41,561 --> 00:21:45,608
you will enter remission faster
and you will survive.

474
00:21:45,652 --> 00:21:47,393
- But...

475
00:21:49,395 --> 00:21:53,573
Then there--there's no way....

476
00:21:53,616 --> 00:21:55,618
I'm never gonna have a baby.

477
00:21:55,662 --> 00:21:58,142
- Hey, look at me.

478
00:21:58,186 --> 00:21:59,709
We will find a way.

479
00:22:06,455 --> 00:22:08,370
Sorry.

480
00:22:08,414 --> 00:22:11,373
I know that there are more
important things than--

481
00:22:11,417 --> 00:22:15,334
but I always dreamed
of having a child.

482
00:22:15,377 --> 00:22:17,248
Yeah, I know that sounds
old-fashioned and--

483
00:22:17,292 --> 00:22:18,815
- No, no, no.

484
00:22:18,859 --> 00:22:21,340
No, it doesn't.

485
00:22:21,383 --> 00:22:23,385
It sounds human.

486
00:22:30,436 --> 00:22:33,177
- Okay, let's play a game.

487
00:22:33,221 --> 00:22:35,484
I will set a task,

488
00:22:35,528 --> 00:22:38,748
and if you complete it,
you win.

489
00:22:38,792 --> 00:22:40,489
- What do I win?

490
00:22:40,533 --> 00:22:42,665
- I am gonna give you

491
00:22:42,709 --> 00:22:45,407
Iggy Bucks.

492
00:22:45,451 --> 00:22:48,149
- Those look lame.
- Well, I'm not done.

493
00:22:48,192 --> 00:22:51,500
Iggy Bucks are how you get
to the real prize.

494
00:22:51,544 --> 00:22:55,548
50 of these earns one hour

495
00:22:55,591 --> 00:22:58,246
with this bad boy.

496
00:22:58,289 --> 00:22:59,900
All right?

497
00:22:59,943 --> 00:23:02,903
It just so happens that
this first task can earn you

498
00:23:02,946 --> 00:23:06,515
all 50 Iggy Bucks in one go.

499
00:23:06,559 --> 00:23:08,648
- What's the task?

500
00:23:08,691 --> 00:23:10,432
- You apologize to your brother.

501
00:23:10,476 --> 00:23:11,825
- No.

502
00:23:11,868 --> 00:23:13,435
- Why not?

503
00:23:13,479 --> 00:23:15,742
- He deserved it.

504
00:23:15,785 --> 00:23:17,657
- Juliet, I know that
you don't feel sorry,

505
00:23:17,700 --> 00:23:21,443
and I know that you may
never feel sorry,

506
00:23:21,487 --> 00:23:24,533
but hurting Calvin
was a big deal.

507
00:23:24,577 --> 00:23:26,666
And a big deal
means a big apology,

508
00:23:26,709 --> 00:23:30,800
but it also means
a big reward.

509
00:23:30,844 --> 00:23:34,151
You in?

510
00:23:34,195 --> 00:23:38,460
- If a big apology
means a big reward...

511
00:23:38,504 --> 00:23:41,158
what about a small apology?

